    <item>
      <title>特鲁多要求石油、天然气生产商减少 35% 的排放量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/trudeau-to-order-oil-gas-producers-to-cut-emissions-by-35</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府将要求加拿大的石油和天然气行业将排放量在 2019 年的基础上减少 35%，这项政策将加剧该国与西部省份的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/trudeau-to-order-oil-gas-producers-to-cut-emissions-by-35</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚将限制投票权以阻止俄罗斯影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/estonia-to-curb-voting-rights-in-bid-to-deter-russian-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚将推进旨在剥夺俄罗斯和白俄罗斯公民在地方选举中投票权的计划，此举旨在打击政府认为的亲克里姆林宫的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/estonia-to-curb-voting-rights-in-bid-to-deter-russian-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:24:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨敦促争吵不休的联盟着眼于切实可行的解决方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/scholz-urges-squabbling-alliance-to-focus-on-practical-solutions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨敦促执政联盟伙伴关注德国面临的挑战的务实解决方案，而不是“意识形态”，并搁置如何帮助欧洲最大经济体走出低迷的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/scholz-urges-squabbling-alliance-to-focus-on-practical-solutions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞安航空首席执行官抨击英国政府提高旅游税“疯狂”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/ryanair-ceo-blasts-bonkers-uk-government-over-travel-duty-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞安航空控股有限公司首席执行官迈克尔奥利里严厉批评英国政府提高航空旅客税的决定，称此举将阻碍经济增长，并促使欧洲最大的低成本航空公司将业务转移到意大利或瑞典等更为包容的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/ryanair-ceo-blasts-bonkers-uk-government-over-travel-duty-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷在联合国就古巴问题投票后，米莱誓言清除“叛徒”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/milei-vows-purge-of-traitors-after-argentina-s-un-vote-on-cuba</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷在联合国投票谴责美国对古巴实施制裁后，总统哈维尔·米莱承诺对阿根廷外交部门进行彻底清洗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/milei-vows-purge-of-traitors-after-argentina-s-un-vote-on-cuba</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油巨头将中东冲突和中国视为首要关注点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/big-oil-chiefs-see-mideast-conflict-and-china-as-top-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些石油业高管表示，中东紧张局势升级以及中美关系是石油巨头面临的最大担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/big-oil-chiefs-see-mideast-conflict-and-china-as-top-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英格兰大学学费明年将因通货膨胀上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/england-university-tuition-fees-to-rise-next-year-with-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于基尔·斯塔默政府试图解决高等教育领域的巨大资金压力，英格兰的大学学费明年将随着通货膨胀而上涨，这是自 2017 年以来的首次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/england-university-tuition-fees-to-rise-next-year-with-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:42:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着以色列紧张局势加剧，伊朗货币贬值至历史最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/iran-s-currency-weakens-to-record-low-as-israel-tension-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者为伊朗伊斯兰共和国与其宿敌以色列之间的军事对峙可能升级做准备，伊朗里亚尔在非监管市场上跌至历史新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/iran-s-currency-weakens-to-record-low-as-israel-tension-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:10:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国就欧盟电动汽车关税向世贸组织提出申诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/china-appeals-to-wto-over-ev-tariffs-imposed-by-european-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国就欧盟对中国电动汽车进口征收的最终关税向世界贸易组织提出诉讼，这一争端进一步升级，使本已紧张的双边关系变得更加紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/china-appeals-to-wto-over-ev-tariffs-imposed-by-european-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 13:03:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法改革法庭之争将墨西哥推向危机边缘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/court-clash-over-judicial-reform-pushes-mexico-to-edge-of-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院对墨西哥司法改革备受争议的举措的审查，势将加剧法官与执政党“复兴党”之间的争斗，有可能将国家推向体制危机的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/court-clash-over-judicial-reform-pushes-mexico-to-edge-of-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
